quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  72,14,"Waanna minna almuslimoonawaminna alqasitoona faman aslama faola-ikataharraw rashada"
  72,15,"Waama alqasitoona fakanoolijahannama hataba"
  72,16,"Waallawi istaqamoo AAala attareeqatilaasqaynahum maan ghadaqa"
  72,17,"Linaftinahum feehi waman yuAArid AAanthikri rabbihi yasluk-hu AAathaban saAAada"
  72,18,"Waanna almasajida lillahi falatadAAoo maAAa Allahi ahada"
  72,19,"Waannahu lamma qama AAabdu AllahiyadAAoohu kadoo yakoonoona AAalayhi libada"
  72,20,"Qul innama adAAoo rabbee walaoshriku bihi ahada"
  72,21,"Qul innee la amliku lakum darranwala rashada"
  72,22,"Qul innee lan yujeeranee mina Allahiahadun walan ajida min doonihi multahada"
  72,23,"Illa balaghan mina Allahiwarisalatihi waman yaAAsi Allahawarasoolahu fa-inna lahu nara jahannama khalideenafeeha abada"
  72,24,"Hatta itha raaw mayooAAadoona fasayaAAlamoona man adAAafu nasiranwaaqallu AAadada"
  72,25,"Qul in adree aqareebun ma tooAAadoonaam yajAAalu lahu rabbee amada"
  72,26,"AAalimu alghaybi fala yuthhiruAAala ghaybihi ahada"
  72,27,"Illa mani irtada min rasoolinfa-innahu yasluku min bayni yadayhi wamin khalfihi rasada"
  72,28,"LiyaAAlama an qad ablaghoo risalatirabbihim waahata bima ladayhim waahsa kullashay-in AAadada"
